snippet.title: Great Game! 1/5 Walkthrough (Game by Tasselfoot) + All 100 Achievement List
snippet.description:
This is a game that I made with Benologist in 3 days.  He did the programming and art, and I yelled at him saying he was doing it all wrong.  It's a meta-game about those wonderful people...  commenters.
